And you go along with
whatever it is she wants to do.

34:50.199 --> 34:54.199
Or commit to taking responsibility
for the next 18 years and beyond.

34:59.600 --> 35:01.400
I should be talking to Ricky, shouldn't I?

35:06.700 --> 35:07.800
I'm sorry, kid.

35:08.500 --> 35:09.600
I'm really sorry.

35:11.700 --> 35:13.500
- About what?
- About everything.

35:14.900 --> 35:16.200
High school stinks.

35:17.500 --> 35:20.200
For some crazy reason, I actually
thought I could make it better.

35:55.400 --> 35:56.900
??? give her a ride?

35:56.900 --> 35:57.900
Why can't someone else?

35:57.900 --> 35:59.600
Maybe I wanna give her a ride.

36:00.000 --> 36:01.800
?? You shouldn't hang out
with girls like that.

36:02.000 --> 36:02.900
Girls like what?

36:02.900 --> 36:04.200
Girls like Amy Juergens.

36:04.600 --> 36:06.200
What's wrong with Amymy Juergens?

36:06.200 --> 36:07.200
Come on, you haven't heard?

36:07.500 --> 36:08.600
Heard what?

36:08.800 --> 36:10.400
Don't you have any girlfriends?

36:10.400 --> 36:12.500
No, I don't. I don't want any girlfriends.

36:12.500 --> 36:14.600
You're not even friends
with the other majorettes?

36:14.600 --> 36:15.800
Not really, no.

36:16.900 --> 36:19.400
They're not as good as I
am, and they know it.

36:19.400 --> 36:21.600
They're jealous, they're
petty, and they're mean.

36:22.100 --> 36:23.800
You never notice how much better I am?

36:24.300 --> 36:27.300
You never notice I do
all the solo performances?

36:27.600 --> 36:29.800
You know, I really don't pay
attention to the baton twirling.

36:29.800 --> 36:31.800
I'm kind of paying attention
to the game, you know?

36:32.600 --> 36:34.200
What's wrong with Amy Juergens?

36:34.200 --> 36:35.800
